  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK725">
<l>āṟṟi ṉaḷavaṟintu kaṟka vavaiyañcā</l>
<l>māṟṟaṅ koṭuttaṟ poruṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In order to reply fearlessly before a foreign court, (ministers) should learn logic according to the rules (of grammar).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
